==English==

===Noun ===

'''collective call sign'''

# {{military}} Any call sign which represents two or more [[facilities]], [[commands]], [[authorities]], or [[units]]. The collective call sign for any of these includes the [[commander]] thereof and all subordinate commanders therein.

## '''''CHARLIE PAPA''''': Command Post of the 1098th Transportation Company (Medium Boat) in Vietnam.
## '''''CHARLIE 34''''': Landing Craft #34 of the 1098th Transportation Company (Medium Boat) in Vietnam.
## '''''CHARLIE 6''''': Commmander of the 1098th Transportation Company (Medium Boat) in Vietnam.

